Class EventLoggerImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventLogger, ItemFeatureEntry

    public class EventLoggerImpl
extends ItemFeatureEntryImpl
implements EventLogger
    An implementation of the model object 'Event Logger'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Log Attributes Change
    • Log Value Change
    • Log Subscription Change
    • Log Writes
